import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"마크다운-사용법"}}>{`마크다운 사용법`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="blockquote" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components} parentName="blockquote">{`마크다운(markdown)은 일반 텍스트 문서의 양식을 편집하는 문법이다. README 파일이나 온라인 문서, 혹은 일반 텍스트 편집기로 문서 양식을 편집할 때 쓰인다. 마크다운을 이용해 작성된 문서는 쉽게 HTML 등 다른 문서형태로 변환이 가능하다.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"우선-깨알-팁"}}>{`📍우선 깨알 팁`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`mac에서 이모지 입력 😁`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`control + command + space
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"문단"}}>{`📍문단`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`문단과 문단 사이는 빈 줄(엔터키 두 번)로 구분한다.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`첫번째 문단

두번째 문단
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`첫번째 문단`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`두번째 문단`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"제목"}}>{`📍제목`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`h1`}</MDXTag>{` 부터 `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`h5`}</MDXTag>{` 까지 제목을 표현할 수 있다.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`# h1
## h2
### h3
#### h4
##### h5
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"인용문"}}>{`📍인용문`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`>`}</MDXTag>{` 블럭인용문자를 이용한다.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`> 인용문
>> 중첩된 인용문
>>> 중중첩된 인용문
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="blockquote" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components} parentName="blockquote">{`인용문`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="blockquote" components={components} parentName="blockquote">
<MDXTag name="p" components={components} parentName="blockquote">{`중첩된 인용문`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="blockquote" components={components} parentName="blockquote">
<MDXTag name="p" components={components} parentName="blockquote">{`중중첩된 인용문`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"목록리스트"}}>{`📍목록(리스트)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"4-1-순서있는-목록번호"}}>{`4-1. 순서있는 목록(번호)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`1. 첫번째
2. 두번째
3. 세번째
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`첫번째`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`두번째`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`세번째`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"4-2-순서없는-목록글머리-기호"}}>{`4-2. 순서없는 목록(글머리 기호)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`- 첫 번째
- 두 번째
- 세 번째
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`첫 번째`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`두 번째`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`세 번째`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"코드-블럭"}}>{`📍코드 블럭`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`\`\`\`javascript
function sum(a, b) {
  return a + b;
}
\`\`\`
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-javascript"}}>{`function sum(a, b) {
  return a + b;
}
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"인라인-코드"}}>{`📍인라인 코드`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`\`yarn install\`
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`yarn install`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"수평선"}}>{`📍수평선`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`---
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="hr" components={components}></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"강조"}}>{`📍강조`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`⌨️ 마크다운`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`*기울여 쓰기*
_기울여쓰기_
**굵게 쓰기**
__굵게 쓰기__
~~취소선~~
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`🖨 실행결과`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="p">{`기울여 쓰기`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="p">{`기울여쓰기`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`굵게 쓰기`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`굵게 쓰기`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="del" components={components} parentName="p">{`취소선`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
